stop \- Stop the current replica group.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\f[B]\f[I]rg.stop()\f[]\f[]
.SH CATEGORY
.PP
ReplicaGroup
.SH "DESCRIPTION"

.sp 2
Stop the current replica group. Operations on the replica group
like creating a node in this group cannot be done after the
replica group is stopped.
.SH "Examples"

.sp 2
